data.description: Bright and spacious end unit townhouse in highly desirable Stonebrook! It is located just minutes away from shopping, dining, schools, parks, and more in every direction! You will be impressed by the vaulted ceilings in the dramatic entryway and living room. The main level also offers an updated kitchen with eating area that opens to the family room with a cozy fireplace, a half bath and laundry area for convenience. Sliding patio doors off the kitchen lead to a spacious deck, great for entertaining. Upstairs, there are two generously sized bedrooms, loft, and one full bath. But wait, there's more!  This home also has a finished English basement perfect for additional living space, a home office, a gym, or whatever suits your needs! Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours - schedule your showing today!
